commit_message:
v0.4.7

Changed the implementation of Step 3, now submits as a cluster job to avoid fatal memory errors with bedtools
made step 3 run as job to fix memory requirement

v0.4.6

fixed issue with GeMoMa where it failed to find the reference genome fasta files

v0.4.5

Fixed issue with Singularity in the BRAKER step

v.0.4.4

fixed bug with GeMoMa when multiple runs were submitted

v 0.4.4

fixed GeMoMa bug when running multiple analyses with different filtering thresholds

v 0.4.3

fixed GeMoMa error when running with multiple filtering thresholds
added step numbers to config file parameters
clarified that genome assembly files must have ".fasta" suffix

Update run_repeatMasker.sh

fixed bug with multithreading

Update config.txt

added warning about RMASK_THREADS parameter

Merge pull request #6 from KrabbenhoftLab/devel

0.4.2 - full migration of the pipeline to the cluster
modified output description for each step

Update run_eggNOG.sh

fixed hardcoded prefix in eggNOG script

Update run_eggNOG.sh

fixed issue where eggNOG output had hardcoded prefix "Engr"
fixed final step - combining repeat masker runs

0.4.2

nextflow for parallelizing step 2 (RepeatMasker) on cluster

Merge pull request #5 from KrabbenhoftLab/devel

output helpful message at end of each step
cluster scripts will now output message at end of run with helpful info

added DIAMOND step

Step 10: RUN DIAMOND AND GET RECIPROCAL BEST HITS
update to bash headers, removed AVX512 constrait

v0.4

allows steps 3 and 4 to be run on the cluster

update for cluster compatibility

removed "--reservation" SBATCH option
added option to resume interrupted RepeatModeler run (step 1)

Update genome-annotation

fixed error in how script was called

added RMODEL_RAM

needed to add RMODEL_RAM to run RepeatModeler on the cluster

v0.3.6

you can now run RepeatModeler on the cluster, using the USE_CLUSTER option in the config file

fixed issue with gemoma

accidentally had ; after GAF.f

fixed error in GeMoMa

 needed to use GAF.f instead of just f for filtering options when calling "GeMoMaPipeline"
changed EVM and eggnog output directory structure
changed PROT_FASTA instructions for BRAKER, needed to play nice with Singularity

v.0.3.4

fixed bug in BRAKER script due to spaces in tsebra config file

Update run_BRAKER.sh

fixed bug due to spaces in tsebra config file
implemented error handling for unset variables
check that all variables in config.txt are set

v 0.3.2

added option to supply custom RNA-seq BAM to GeMoMa

Option for annotation without RNA-seq

HISAT2 now optional, BRAKER will automatically  choose between RNA+protein or protein-only mode

added new step 9

added functional annotation step with eggNOG mapper
